    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Work in Batches\n\nLoop controller — releases 20 item(s) per pass. Output 2 (loop) processes the batch, output 1 (done) fires after the last batch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Aggregate Batch Results · ②→ Process Batch Item",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
        "color": 2
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
