      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Mark Completed in Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Sort Jobs Newest First · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account",
